OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fmostly clear eastwards early in the
OL,7,Fevening, although remaining cloudy for
OL,8,Fmuch of the night with perhaps a few
OL,9,Fdrizzly patches at times. Staying mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FMostly cloudy on Friday with a
OL,12,Ffew drizzly outbreaks possible in the
OL,13,Fmorning, but many areas remaining dry.
OL,14,FBreezy, especially along the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,17,FGenerally dry through this period with
OL,18,Fpatchy cloud and sunny spells. Breezy
OL,19,Fon Saturday but winds falling light
OL,20,Ffor Sunday and Monday. Feeling warm,
OL,21,Fespecially in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
